10%, 20%, and by intensity, I
mean the depth of the breath

01:08:12.020 --> 01:08:14.400
and the speed of the breath.

01:08:14.400 --> 01:08:16.520
Let it be more than before.

01:08:42.180 --> 01:08:44.850
Continue.

01:08:44.850 --> 01:08:45.960
Excellent.

01:08:45.960 --> 01:08:50.929
Now, at least 30 times more
powerful than what it was.

01:09:05.359 --> 01:09:10.819
The speed to whatever it
is that is comfortable,

01:09:10.819 --> 01:09:15.410
the strength to whatever
it is that is comfortable,

01:09:15.410 --> 01:09:20.540
and a simple thought that I
am grateful to myself for all

01:09:20.540 --> 01:09:22.460
that I'm going to achieve.

01:09:41.510 --> 01:09:43.210
Excellent.

01:09:43.210 --> 01:09:44.569
Relax.

01:09:44.569 --> 01:09:47.510
Open your eyes.

01:09:47.510 --> 01:09:49.840
Smile.

01:09:49.840 --> 01:09:51.460
Try smiling.

01:09:51.460 --> 01:09:53.560
Smiling is nice.

01:09:53.560 --> 01:09:54.730
Yes.

01:09:54.730 --> 01:09:56.380
How are you feeling?

01:09:56.380 --> 01:09:58.480
Say, I'm feeling very good.

01:09:58.480 --> 01:10:01.930
Saying that I'm feeling
good is half the battle won.

01:10:01.930 --> 01:10:04.720
How are you feeling?

01:10:04.720 --> 01:10:05.760
Please say it.

01:10:05.760 --> 01:10:07.930
Let me hear you.

01:10:07.930 --> 01:10:13.390
Yes, I am feeling good, and
I thank myself for all the

01:10:13.390 --> 01:10:18.660
better that I am
going to achieve.

01:10:18.660 --> 01:10:21.174
Finally, in the end,
what I would like to say

01:10:21.174 --> 01:10:26.987
is we are living a
life of patterns.

01:10:30.260 --> 01:10:36.070
And when we live our
life, we can either

01:10:36.070 --> 01:10:42.172
reinforce our old patterns,
or we can create new patterns.

01:10:46.110 --> 01:10:53.610
Living a life, as I said, of
not being aware of the goal

01:10:53.610 --> 01:10:58.320
and being away from
peace and relaxation

01:10:58.320 --> 01:11:03.900
reinforces the previous patterns
that we make in our life.

01:11:03.900 --> 01:11:07.710
And the pattern can be anything.

01:11:07.710 --> 01:11:11.580
I cannot love the
way I used to love.

01:11:11.580 --> 01:11:15.150
I was more motivated
when I was younger.

01:11:15.150 --> 01:11:17.370
I do not know--

01:11:17.370 --> 01:11:21.480
whatever pattern
that we have made.

01:11:21.480 --> 01:11:25.770
And through our choices and
our decisions and our actions,

01:11:25.770 --> 01:11:27.750
you can only do
things in your life.

01:11:27.750 --> 01:11:30.930
Trust me, there is nothing else.

01:11:30.930 --> 01:11:34.590
One is we can
reinforce the patterns,

01:11:34.590 --> 01:11:39.090
or we have the power
to start creating what?

01:11:39.090 --> 01:11:39.735
New patterns.

01:11:42.370 --> 01:11:46.330
Of course, I can do
push-ups, but if I

01:11:46.330 --> 01:11:48.300
don't do push-ups,
then every day,

01:11:48.300 --> 01:11:50.880
I am reinforcing
the pattern of what?

01:11:50.880 --> 01:11:54.910
That I can't do or cannot--

01:11:54.910 --> 01:11:56.270
please mind my English.

01:11:56.270 --> 01:11:58.250
It is not my first language.

01:11:58.250 --> 01:11:59.501
I cannot do push-ups.

01:12:03.350 --> 01:12:06.490
The second thing that I can do--
start doing one push-up today

01:12:06.490 --> 01:12:11.481
so that tomorrow, I can
create a new pattern.

01:12:11.481 --> 01:12:11.980
Why?

01:12:11.980 --> 01:12:14.020
Because my body
is very adaptable.

01:12:14.020 --> 01:12:18.400
My body is very
beautiful, and my body

01:12:18.400 --> 01:12:19.905
is very sensitive to growth.

01:12:23.550 --> 01:12:29.800
And if I choose
to reinvent, then

01:12:29.800 --> 01:12:33.670
I have the power
and the capacity

01:12:33.670 --> 01:12:38.440
to upgrade my inner software
in such a fantastic manner

01:12:38.440 --> 01:12:42.610
that every day, I am
creating new patterns

01:12:42.610 --> 01:12:44.630
in which to live my life.

01:12:44.630 --> 01:12:48.020
But these patterns are
not the numbing patterns,

01:12:48.020 --> 01:12:52.300
but the relaxing and
the peaceful patterns.

01:12:52.300 --> 01:12:54.530
And the beginning
is, the start is

01:12:54.530 --> 01:12:56.230
the three things that I said.

01:12:56.230 --> 01:12:59.350
The first thing-- one are
before you go to sleep,

01:12:59.350 --> 01:13:01.020
no electronics.

01:13:01.020 --> 01:13:01.620
Let's start.

01:13:01.620 --> 01:13:04.700
Let's see what happens.

01:13:04.700 --> 01:13:07.030
15 minutes before
you go to sleep,

01:13:07.030 --> 01:13:12.110
take out your golden
book, per se, and write.

01:13:12.110 --> 01:13:13.340
What is it I want?

01:13:13.340 --> 01:13:15.680
Why do I want it?

01:13:15.680 --> 01:13:18.250
What will I get, if I get it?

01:13:18.250 --> 01:13:23.460
And what is the price
I'm going to pay?

01:13:23.460 --> 01:13:25.700
Five minutes before
I go to sleep,

01:13:25.700 --> 01:13:28.710
I just relax, and
I just contemplate,

01:13:28.710 --> 01:13:31.110
and I just connect
with my breath,

01:13:31.110 --> 01:13:34.140
and my breath, the three
most important things--

01:13:34.140 --> 01:13:39.030
deep, continuous, and little bit
so that your breath is acting

01:13:39.030 --> 01:13:41.042
like white noise for yourself.

01:13:44.850 --> 01:13:51.530
And finally, when you get up,
take out the time to go out,

01:13:51.530 --> 01:13:58.860
and at least five, 10 minutes,
again, this breath, awareness

01:13:58.860 --> 01:14:03.750
of this breath, awareness of the
thought, and the contemplation,

01:14:03.750 --> 01:14:07.500
and at the same time, I am good.

01:14:07.500 --> 01:14:12.085
And I thank myself for all
the time going to achieve.

01:14:14.640 --> 01:14:15.140
Why?

01:14:15.140 --> 01:14:20.930
Because you see our
bodies are so very simple.

01:14:20.930 --> 01:14:25.650
And final experiment on
how simple our body is--

01:14:28.510 --> 01:14:32.680
my friend, Jay,
took me to a place--

01:14:32.680 --> 01:14:34.748
I don't know where--

01:14:34.748 --> 01:14:39.460
where they give you two
cookies, vegan cookies.

01:14:39.460 --> 01:14:43.180
And they put very nice ice
cream in between the cookie.

01:14:43.180 --> 01:14:45.190
It is the most
fantastic alliance

01:14:45.190 --> 01:14:48.920
I have ever seen since
the sun and the moon.

01:14:48.920 --> 01:14:51.950
I never had thought-- have
you ever eaten cookie and ice

01:14:51.950 --> 01:14:53.150
cream?

01:14:53.150 --> 01:14:53.810
Yes or no?

01:14:53.810 --> 01:14:54.480
All of you?

01:14:54.480 --> 01:14:54.980
No.

01:14:54.980 --> 01:14:59.050
If you haven't, what have
you done with your life?

01:14:59.050 --> 01:15:01.890
So what I want you to do is
imagine that cookie and ice

01:15:01.890 --> 01:15:06.390
cream of your most favorite
cookie that you have ever eaten

01:15:06.390 --> 01:15:09.850
and the most favorite ice cream
that you have ever imagined,

01:15:09.850 --> 01:15:13.720
and put it in front of you.

01:15:13.720 --> 01:15:16.810
And maybe the cookies
are hot and gooey,

01:15:16.810 --> 01:15:18.530
fresh out of the oven.

01:15:18.530 --> 01:15:20.530
And the ice cream is cold.

01:15:20.530 --> 01:15:23.260
And both of them are
sort of together,

01:15:23.260 --> 01:15:25.540
and you put them in your mouth.

01:15:25.540 --> 01:15:27.340
And when you put
them in your mouth,

01:15:27.340 --> 01:15:29.950
you are biting into the
cookie, and the cookie

01:15:29.950 --> 01:15:32.110
is mixing with the ice cream.

01:15:32.110 --> 01:15:36.550
And it slowly starts to
swirl and merge into one,

01:15:36.550 --> 01:15:39.770
and then you inhale
and take it inside.

01:15:39.770 --> 01:15:44.700
And then-- forget about then.

01:15:44.700 --> 01:15:46.800
What I want to ask you--

01:15:46.800 --> 01:15:51.240
how many people's mouths
start to water when I explain

01:15:51.240 --> 01:15:54.260
the cookie and the ice cream?

01:15:54.260 --> 01:15:57.660
Was there a little bit
of saliva in your mouth?

01:15:57.660 --> 01:15:58.940
Yes or no?

01:15:58.940 --> 01:16:00.030
If yes, you are human.

01:16:00.030 --> 01:16:05.100
If not, I don't know
which planet you are from.

01:16:05.100 --> 01:16:09.000
But imagine this is how simple
and beautiful our mind is.

01:16:09.000 --> 01:16:11.332
There is no cookie and ice
cream, at least not here,

01:16:11.332 --> 01:16:13.170
not right now.

01:16:13.170 --> 01:16:14.910
I am not that kind
of a monk, who

01:16:14.910 --> 01:16:18.150
will do like this and
cookie and ice cream.

01:16:18.150 --> 01:16:21.810
And your mind knows there is
no cookie and ice cream yet.

01:16:21.810 --> 01:16:24.841
Your mind salivates as
if it is about to come.

01:16:24.841 --> 01:16:28.280
Yes or no?

01:16:28.280 --> 01:16:32.450
Tell me, my dear, reciprocate.

01:16:32.450 --> 01:16:34.610
Yes or no?

01:16:34.610 --> 01:16:41.390
So if your mind can drool to an
imaginary cookie and ice cream,

01:16:41.390 --> 01:16:45.050
then I want you to imagine
how many of your reactions

01:16:45.050 --> 01:16:49.730
are to imaginary stimuluses
or stimulants or--

01:16:49.730 --> 01:16:50.400
I don't know.

01:16:50.400 --> 01:16:54.320
You get it.

01:16:54.320 --> 01:16:59.980
And that is why if
our reactions are

01:16:59.980 --> 01:17:05.900
going to be so many
imaginary stimulants,

01:17:05.900 --> 01:17:10.710
then why not somewhere
I start to tell myself

01:17:10.710 --> 01:17:17.080
that I thank myself for all
that I am going to achieve?

01:17:17.080 --> 01:17:22.760
Maybe that peace will give
me the power to work hard,

01:17:22.760 --> 01:17:25.800
and maybe, in
time, truly achieve

01:17:25.800 --> 01:17:28.840
whatever it is I am capable of.

01:17:31.690 --> 01:17:35.210
And the final thing
that I can request

01:17:35.210 --> 01:17:41.910
to you is one of the
most powerful tools

01:17:41.910 --> 01:17:45.070
is the most active
form of meditation

01:17:45.070 --> 01:17:48.510
and sometimes the toughest.

01:17:48.510 --> 01:17:51.372
Do I have permission
from you to share?

01:17:54.140 --> 01:17:57.130
This is the secret ingredient.

01:17:57.130 --> 01:18:01.020
This is the chemical
X used by professor

01:18:01.020 --> 01:18:03.590
to make Power Puff Girls.

01:18:03.590 --> 01:18:08.200
This is the most important Kung
Fu Panda dragon scroll secret

01:18:08.200 --> 01:18:09.360
that I'm about to tell you.

01:18:11.930 --> 01:18:13.670
And the secret is--

01:18:13.670 --> 01:18:14.900
in fact, it's not a secret.

01:18:14.900 --> 01:18:20.070
It's something that
sort of helps me,

01:18:20.070 --> 01:18:25.190
may help you, a form
of active meditation.

01:18:25.190 --> 01:18:30.350
And the secret is I
want you to learn to--

01:18:30.350 --> 01:18:34.930
drum roll-- smile.

01:18:34.930 --> 01:18:36.716
It's very beautiful.

01:18:36.716 --> 01:18:37.216
Try.

01:18:37.216 --> 01:18:37.716
Smile.

01:18:40.660 --> 01:18:42.810
Try, please.

01:18:42.810 --> 01:18:43.580
Yes.

01:18:43.580 --> 01:18:46.781
All of you, smile.

01:18:46.781 --> 01:18:49.030
And how you will practice
this, the first thing you'll

01:18:49.030 --> 01:18:51.730
do when you go early
in the morning,

01:18:51.730 --> 01:18:52.900
you will look in the mirror.

01:18:52.900 --> 01:18:55.570
And what you are going to
do is look at whatever face

01:18:55.570 --> 01:18:57.970
you are seeing, and you
will smile at that person

01:18:57.970 --> 01:19:00.870
that you are awesome.

01:19:00.870 --> 01:19:01.870
Can you do that?

01:19:01.870 --> 01:19:03.040
I want you to try.

01:19:03.040 --> 01:19:03.540
Trust me.

01:19:03.540 --> 01:19:06.000
It is the most
fantastic thing when

01:19:06.000 --> 01:19:09.090
you are looking in the mirror
and not pulling in your stomach

01:19:09.090 --> 01:19:12.390
and not thinking how I would
look if this would happen

01:19:12.390 --> 01:19:16.080
or that would happen or if
I was fairer or I was darker

01:19:16.080 --> 01:19:19.560
or if my hair was longer
or lesser, or I don't know.

01:19:19.560 --> 01:19:22.020
Just look at the person you
see in the mirror, and say,

01:19:22.020 --> 01:19:23.243
you are awesome.

01:19:26.350 --> 01:19:28.450
And then continue
to practice this.

01:19:28.450 --> 01:19:30.760
When you are driving,
somebody looks at you

01:19:30.760 --> 01:19:33.460
while you are
driving, no need to--

01:19:33.460 --> 01:19:35.500
try.

01:19:35.500 --> 01:19:36.790
Let's see what happens.

01:19:36.790 --> 01:19:38.680
Maybe that person smiles back.

01:19:38.680 --> 01:19:41.620
Maybe that person gives you
some universal gestures.

01:19:41.620 --> 01:19:42.610
How do I care?

01:19:42.610 --> 01:19:45.070
But I am not smiling
for that person.

01:19:45.070 --> 01:19:46.810
I am smiling,
because my brain is

01:19:46.810 --> 01:19:49.900
so simple that if I look
at imaginary cookie,

01:19:49.900 --> 01:19:50.680
my brain drools.

01:19:53.190 --> 01:19:58.140
And if I give my brain a
conditioning to be happy,

01:19:58.140 --> 01:19:59.190
then trust me.

01:19:59.190 --> 01:20:02.610
My brain do not know it
is such a simple thing.

01:20:02.610 --> 01:20:04.730
My biology don't know.

01:20:04.730 --> 01:20:09.760
It thinks the cookie is real,
and that will give me the power

01:20:09.760 --> 01:20:15.700
to focus, to function in the
most appropriate and beautiful

01:20:15.700 --> 01:20:16.530
manner.

01:20:16.530 --> 01:20:21.460
Maybe the easiest way to
break the desensitization,

01:20:21.460 --> 01:20:25.000
and be in the moment
of where you are

01:20:25.000 --> 01:20:29.490
is accepting that I am good.

01:20:29.490 --> 01:20:37.190
And finally, I thank myself for
all the time going to achieve.

01:20:37.190 --> 01:20:43.750
So I thank all of you,
and I smile at all of you.

01:20:43.750 --> 01:20:47.190
And I hope you are
happy listening

01:20:47.190 --> 01:20:50.770
to what I had to share.

01:20:50.770 --> 01:20:56.530
And I hope that all of you find
the real happiness, but most

01:20:56.530 --> 01:21:00.070
of all, the peace
and relaxation that

01:21:00.070 --> 01:21:05.020
are the most beautiful
forms of human existence.

01:21:05.020 --> 01:21:08.620
And I hope, and I
wish that all of you

01:21:08.620 --> 01:21:13.030
feel the euphoria that
I was talking about--

01:21:13.030 --> 01:21:17.170
maybe in your work, maybe
in your relationships,

01:21:17.170 --> 01:21:21.820
maybe in whichever form
you wish to experience it,

01:21:21.820 --> 01:21:27.500
because I believe we, humanity,
are a collective consciousness.

01:21:27.500 --> 01:21:32.300
And if all of us are
resonating at a high frequency,

01:21:32.300 --> 01:21:34.930
then the whole planet is healed.

01:21:34.930 --> 01:21:38.170
And even if a part
of the body is sick,

01:21:38.170 --> 01:21:40.390
then the whole body
feels the pain.

01:21:40.390 --> 01:21:44.560
In the same manner, even if
part of collective consciousness

01:21:44.560 --> 01:21:48.070
is hurt or in pain,
then the whole planet

01:21:48.070 --> 01:21:51.370
feels in some
manner or the other.

01:21:51.370 --> 01:21:54.040
And that is why I like to talk.

01:21:54.040 --> 01:21:57.130
I like to come all
the way from wherever

01:21:57.130 --> 01:22:01.660
to here, San Francisco, to
speak to the kind and good

01:22:01.660 --> 01:22:04.570
and gentlemen and gentlewomen
that are sitting in front

01:22:04.570 --> 01:22:10.360
of me, because I
seek that one day

01:22:10.360 --> 01:22:14.740
through our collective
efforts and endurance,

01:22:14.740 --> 01:22:17.190
the whole collective
consciousness will

01:22:17.190 --> 01:22:21.410
be very, very good.

01:22:21.410 --> 01:22:23.100
So thank you.

01:22:23.100 --> 01:22:26.480
I thank you, and I
thank the infinity that

01:22:26.480 --> 01:22:29.510
resides amongst all of you.

01:22:29.510 --> 01:22:34.010
And I hope, and I pray,
and I bless that all of you

01:22:34.010 --> 01:22:36.155
achieve all that you seek.

